It also does not include when a policy has support from conservatives but of course will mention liberal opposition. Reuters singles out President Trump by often saying said President Trump without providing evidence yet for every other politician in the world including the Chinese premier and Khomeni, Reuters does not mention them not providing evidence for their statements which no one actually does.
